	<h1 class="title">这个天花板“滚来滚去”的凉亭，我大概能看上一下午</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/101857/small/101857.jpg?1429073860" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">谢舒敏 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-08-25 13:38:19 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/13956/medium/13956.jpg?1440477887" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="13956" data-title="《这个天花板“滚来滚去”的凉亭，我大概能看上一下午》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/13956/medium/13956.jpg?1440477887" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/13956.html?from=timeline&amp;isappinstalled=1" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
